Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ten years after Tet, February 1978
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brrr
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Feb 1978
Ten years after Tet offensive. US public opinion shifts over foreign affairs. Muhammed Ali defeated as reigning world heavyweight boxing champion by Leon Spinks. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less